    "name": "BillApp API - Local Testing",
    "description": "Complete API collection for BillApp (Spring Boot + JWT). Base URL: http://localhost:8080\n\n## Quick Start\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Import the BillApp Environment\n3. Run **Auth / Login** first — JWT token auto-saves\n4. All other requests use the saved token automatically\n\n## Default Credentials\n- Username: admin\n- Password: admin123",
